&lt;li&gt;Observes each machine to verify quality performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sets and adjusts necessary configurations for equipment operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Used machines are properly cleaned to company standards prior to delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist supplies and equipment delivery team as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs other related duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load, unload, deliver copiers and copier products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow routes and time schedule&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate and inspect a delivery box truck&lt;/li&gt;
